Package: RAiddin
Title: Agentic Claude Chat Panel for RStudio
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Mirko", "Daga", email = "mirko.daga.21@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An RStudio addin that provides an agentic Claude AI chat panel
    with code execution, output capture, and plot vision capabilities.
    Supports a hybrid execution model using evaluate (main session) and
    callr (isolated subprocess), with codetools-based dependency analysis
    for selective environment replication.
